      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PRECIOUS COOKIE (7) jumped from a squeeze box last start but was quickly into stride and led throughout to score (20.05) at this track in a Maiden over 350m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Hard to go past. WHISKEY MY WAY (1) held his own to the line last start and filled a minor placing, beaten only a neck (19.62) behind Hocking at Q Straight. The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Winning chance. EBONY VALLEY (8) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at her last five runs. Last start finished 2nd on May 24 over 350m at this track behind Power Valley beaten 3 lengths (20.16) in a Grade 5. Expected to feature. OUR MIRACLES (5) was in the money last start and likely to feature again.",
